Package gameobjects.staticobjects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DestroyableStaticObject
    A DestroyableStaticObject is a StaticObject that as the special ability of being destroyed by the players bomb.
    Door
    A Door is a StaticObject used to go from a Room to another upon collision by the player with a opened one.
    Poop
    A Poop is a DestroyableStaticObject, that can both be destroyed by Tears and Bombs.
    Rock
    A rock is a StaticObject that is just used to block the player.
    Spike
    A Spike is a StaticObject that is just used to damage the player.
    Stair
    A Stair is a StaticObject that is just to send the player to the next floor.
    StaticObject
    A StaticObject is a GameObject that as the special ability of being able to block or damage the other objects that collides with it.
    Wall
    A Wall is a StaticObject used to delimit the room.
